ads and a section on </span><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/moonglettes-savory-lentil-pancakes/"><span>lentils</span></a><span style="font-weight:400"> and soups, to </span><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/sleep-moon-milk/"><span>drinks</span></a><span style="font-weight:400"> and desserts, there is a ton that the whole family will surely love. The hardcover is currently 26 per cent off. </span></p>
